            <td width="366" align="left" valign="top">
<p>BA Continuum Costa Rica and BA Continuum Mexico are non-bank subsidiaries of Bank of America that provide contact centers, shared services and technology solutions to Bank of America customers, but also to associates based around the world:  from the U.S. to Asia and in Latin America. While referring to BA Continuum, we are referring to both organizations. </p>

<p>Bank of America teammates in Costa Rica and Mexico support multiple product lines, including Home Loans & Insurance, and Consumer and Commercial Banking. This includes back-office operations and transactions, customer support and service functions, technology support and services, general human resource functions, business planning and general financial services. </p>

<p>At BA Continuum, associates are part of a diverse, global banking environment with best-in-class people, processes and practices. Associates belong to a globally admired brand, which is one of the largest financial institutions in the world.</p>
<div id="LinesOfBusiness"></div>
<h2>Lines of Business</h2>
<p>BA Continuum Mexico & Costa Rica offer customized solutions and operational expertise to support a wide range of business functions from HL&I, CSBB and GTO, such as: </p>
<p>
<ul>
<li>Customer Advocacy & Collections</li>
<li>Credit Cards - Customer Assistance</li>
<li>Fraud Services</li>
<li>CS&S Deposit </li>
<li>Capacity Planning - Distributed</li>
<li>Data Management Organization</li>
<li>Global Access Operations</li>
<li>Global Quality Monitoring </li>
</ul>
